809
00:52:29,000 --> 00:52:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] No, no.

810
00:52:30,000 --> 00:52:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja verim uvijek šta je statistika.

811
00:52:33,000 --> 00:52:36,000
