813
00:52:38,000 --> 00:52:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima tako lepi sjećanje.

814
00:52:40,000 --> 00:52:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja šedampu tesećan.

815
00:52:42,000 --> 00:52:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja svakom navijaču i Dinama.

816
00:52:44,000 --> 00:52:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo već u Dinama.

817
00:52:45,000 --> 00:52:47,000
